               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18341205-name-149" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18341205-name-149" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18341205-name-149" type="surname" value="FOXCROFT"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18341205-name-149" type="given" value="JOHN GEORGE"></interp>JOHN GEORGE FOXCROFT</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Soley-terrace, Claremont-square, Pentonville. On the afternoon of the 28th of November, I was walking in Smithfield, near the end of Giltspur-street—I felt something at my pocket—turned, and saw the prisoner with my handkerchief in his hand—I col<lb></lb>lared him, and gave him to the policeman—he threw the handkerchief down—another boy picked it up and gave it to me—this is it.</p>
