               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">JURY</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">to</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">JOHN GEORGE FOXCROFT</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> How is it the boy is not here, who picked up the handkerchief? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> I let him go, thinking I could not take them both—I suppose he was an accomplice—the prisoner's mother bears a good character.</p>
               <p>The prisoner put in a written defence, stating that he had found the handkerchief on the ground.</p>
